      <title>壳牌前首席执行官谈论在纽约上市的好处</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-09/former-shell-ceo-talks-up-benefits-of-listing-in-new-york</link>
      <description><![CDATA[壳牌公司前首席执行官表示，在美国上市的国际石油公司受益于更高的市盈率、更多的融资渠道和更友好的投资者基础。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-09/former-shell-ceo-talks-up-benefits-of-listing-in-new-york</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Apr 2024 10:11:49 GMT</pubDate>
